ts.com/media/uploads/p/xxl/294222-7_2-origami-so-soft-3-ply-toilet-tissue.jpg"}],"variable_weight":null,"brand":{"name":"Origami","slug":"origami","url":"/pb/origami/"},"additional_attr":{"bby_lod":null,"info":[]},"tabs":[{"content":"<style type=\"text/css\"> @import url(\"https://www.bbassets.com/static/froala_style_v2.min.css\"); </style>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'ProximaNova-Regular';font-size:13px;line-height: 18px;color:8f8f8f;\">\n            <p>Origami Toilet Paper Rolls: 100% cellulose fibre for an eco-friendly, premium finish. Thick and super-soft, suitable for all skin types, both for adults and children. Versatile for quick clean-ups, providing a luxurious bathroom experience. Highly absorbent, flushable, fits standard holders. Hygienic and safe to use. Free from dyes, fragrances, and optical brightening agents. Ideal for your family's needs</p>\n        </div>","title":"About the Product"},{"content":"<style type=\"text/css\"> @import url(\"https://www.bbassets.com/static/froala_style_v2.min.css\"); </style>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'ProximaNova-Regular';font-size:13px;line-height: 18px;color:8f8f8f;\">\n            <ul><li>Material: Paper</li><li>Features: Soft, absorbent, and strong; designed for comfort and durability</li><li>Type: Standard toilet paper roll</li><li>Colour: White</li><li>Number of Units: 12 rolls x 160 Pulls each = 1920 Pulls</li><li>Brand: Origami</li><li>Sheet Size: Standard</li></ul>\n        </div>","title":"Specification"},{"content":"<style type=\"text/css\"> @import url(\"https://www.bbassets.com/static/froala_style_v2.min.css\"); </style>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'ProximaNova-Regular';font-size:13px;line-height: 18px;color:8f8f8f;\">\n            <ul><li>Extra soft and highly absorbent: The extra soft material makes for efficient and smooth cleaning.</li><li>Safe and hygienic: Our toilet paper is perfect for all members of the family.</li><li>Made from 100% cellulose fibre: Free of any inks, dyes, harsh chemicals, and optical brightening agents.</li><li>Easily disposable: Designed to be easily degradable with no harm to the environment. It won't create clogs or blockages in drains, ensuring hassle-free disposal.</li><li>Pack contains: 3-ply toilet tissue paper roll - 160 pulls x pack of 12 = 1920 Pulls&nbsp;</li></ul>\n        </div>","title":"Benefits"},{"content":"<style type=\"text/css\"> @import url(\"https://www.bbassets.com/static/froala_style_v2.min.css\"); </style>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'ProximaNova-Regular';font-size:13px;line-height: 18px;color:8f8f8f;\">\n            <ul><li>Use as needed: Tear off the amount needed for personal hygiene purposes.</li><li>Handle gently: Avoid excessive tearing or pulling to ensure smooth use.</li><li>Dispose after use: Flush used tissue down the toilet or dispose of it in the trash, following local disposal guidelines.</li></ul>\n        </div>","title":"How to Use"},{"content":"<style type=\"text/css\"> @import url(\"https://www.bbassets.com/static/froala_style_v2.min.css\"); </style>\n        <div style=\"font-family: 'ProximaNova-Regular';font-size:13px;line-height: 18px;color:8f8f8f;\">\n            <p>EAN Code: 294222 <br>Manufacturer Name &amp; Marketed by Address: Origami Cellulo Private Limited,126 A,Sriranga Complex,Ashwath Nagar,Bengaluru-560094 <br>Country of Origin:India <br></p><p>  <br></p><p> For Queries/Feedback/Complaints, Contact our customer care executive at 1860 123 1000 | Address: Innovative Retail Concepts Private Limited, Ranka Junction 4th Floor, Tin Factory Bus Stop. KR Puram, Bangalore-560016, Email: customerservice@bigbasket.com</p>\n        </div>","title":"Other Product Info"}],"tags":[{"header":"COUNTRY OF ORIGIN","values":[{"display_name":"India","dest_type":"product_list","dest_slug":"type=tag&slug=country-of-origin--india","url":"/ts/173/country-of-origin/india"}]},{"header":"COLOUR","values":[{"display_name":"White","dest_type":"product_list","dest_slug":"type=tag&slu